title: Leicester lazy stars’ pitiful lack of fight means they are at risk of ruining their Premier League title legacy
text:
EFL IAN WRIGHT Leicester lazy stars’ pitiful lack of fight means they are at risk of ruining their Premier League title legacy 
Nine months ago they wrote a footballing fairy-tale the like of which we will never see again... now it's a distant memory Comment
